# Euler's Method Web App

This C-based WebAssembly application uses Tinyexpr to parse a scalar function input to approximate values of said function at a given x using Euler's Method, a primitive technique of approximating a function at a given x using its derivative. This calculator also uses Emscripten to compile C code into Wasm for efficiency.
